values:
im tired of feeling like my best friends aren't even there for me anymore.
the only people i know i can talk to about everything anymore are shawna and romell.
what is so wrong with this guy?
i can't believe you guys are gonna listen to some stupid rumors. 
i didn't think you were like that.
but i honestly dont care.
i like him!
i like the texts in the morning saying good morning.
i like the random comments like "you're such a dork!" or "you have really pretty eyes.'
aren't friends suppose to be happy for their best friends no matter what.
and i mean you're even talking behind my back.
you'd think if you were my true best friends that you would atleast confront me bout it.
oh excuse me; one of you did. but now you won't listen.
shawna is happy for me cause she just likes to see me happy.
romell has got my back and has told me if this guy hurts me he'll be there for me.
but what about you guys? you just talk behind my back. what kind of friends are you?
i don't care what you think whatsoever.
he is amazing! and the fact that i can be me with him and i've never even talked to him before makes me happy.
why can't you just be happy cause im happy?
this is the first guy in forever that has ever made me feel like i am more than i am
like i couldn't be any happier.
and you want to just be bitches behind my back.
im tired of this and im sorry
but for once i don't care how you feel.
i might like you kid. :)

so here i am again.
thinking about someone all the time.
wondering if he's thinking about me too.
getting in trouble for talking to him all the time instead of doing my homework.
in a hurry to see him but then holding on to the very last second til i have to say goodbye.
late night conversations about the most randomest things ever.
friends that keep telling us how cute we are together.
jealous people that wish they were as amazing and happy as us.
the best hugs in the world!!
someone to make me feel ten times better just by being there.
someone to make me so mad when he is stupid but for some reason i can't seem to hate him.
laughing and smiling all the time and wondering why the heck my cheeks are always hurting.
having people question me every day if he's asked; and then watching them get frustrated when i say no. lol
those wonderful afternoon walks to my locker.
those stupid butterflies in the stomach that don't seem to go away.
someone there to make me laugh by calling me good-looking even when i look like crap.
i must be the luckiest girl in the world,the solarsystem,the universe!
this kid is the only reason i look foward to school anymore.
thank goodness for that note in the library. <3

so this kid makes me smile BIG TIME. be jealous; we're amazing!!
too bad i don't even know if he LIKES me; maybe you can let me know what you think. :P

man today was amazing.
the pep rally was HOT!!!
but we kept dancing when our music stopped so everything went fabulous.
gosh; i don't think i have ever had to count that loud in my life.
i was completely out of breath. lol.
oh man; this kid though.
i may get some bad comments but he makes me smile.
he is totally sweet and i really think i might like him.. A LOT. :P
oh and i also realized i had known from the beginning that that other crap wasn't gonna work.
i mean we come from too totally different crowds and have very little in common.
and friends can't work for the same reason. duh.
plus he was like everyone warned me. haha.
goodness gracious.
i believe this year is gonna be a good one.
atleast it better be.
i am so excited cause i have some pretty amazing people in my life. :]

AMAZING!!!

so basically i am loving life.
besides a kid that just doesn't seem to get it;
my life is making me smile.. big time!
i have come to find i have some pretty amazing best friends.
one new one that i just couldn't do without.
then i kinda think i might like this other guy;
i mean he just seems so sweet;
but the people that i've told don't seem to like that idea.
who knows!
i made level 12; which is pretty exciting.
no i'm not bragging i am just releaved to finally have gotten to the top after years of trying.
driving and having freedom is wonderful.
people say; oh you just turned 16, life is still the same.
well maybe to you; but i love having my license. lol.
everything just seems right right now.
i mean i even have a fabulous husband; make that two. :]

hehe. i live to smile.

so life has been twisted; flipped; and turned all the way around.
                its like nothing makes much sense anymore.
    i mean i have so many friends and tons of people that care about me.
                i have tons of guys for once that really like me and i like some of them too.
    so tell me why it bothers me that i messed stuff up and you won't even talk to me now.
        tell me why it bothers me that i don't have you to laugh at and have you make fun of me.
        tell me why it bothers me that i don't have you to tell all these stupid things that happen to me so you can laugh at me.
        tell me why it bothers me that i do have so many other friends; but none of them crack me up like you do.
        tell me why it bothers me that you aren't there to say "yes" anymore; in that crazy weird way that makes me smile.
        tell me why it bothers me that we went from talking all the time to giving these weird looks to each other in the hallway.
        tell me why it bothers me that i know we could hate each other and never talk to each other again and the world wouldn't end; yet i could 
                                                      care less cause i don't want us to never talk again; that won't work for me.
        tell me why it bothers me.

i know everything would be fine if we never spoke again but that doesn't matter to me. i miss the way you could crack me up and get me laughingfor hours even after we got off the phone[bet ya didn't know that]. i miss that guy that i could tell all the stupid things that had happened to me and he would just make fun of me and crack up laughing. i miss that guy that became one of the best friends i've ever had until i screwed things up. i know we could hate each other forever; but honestly i need this kid as my friend. i need them phone calls again every now and then to keep me sane. i just wish it didn't feel like waiting for him to understand and realize what i'm saying is like waiting for the rain to fall in this drought.
